					<div class="engagement-icon">‚ö°</div>
					<h3>Active Lifestyle</h3>
					<div class="activity-tags">
						<span class="activity-tag martial">ü•ã Karate</span>
						<span class="activity-tag martial">ü•ä Boxing</span>
